Package com.example.hashcache.models

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CodeLocation
    Represents the location where a code was scanned
    CodeMetadata
    A class representing metadata for a scannable code.
    Comment
    Represents a comment left by a player
    ContactInfo
    Contains the contact information for a player
    Coordinate
    Represents a coordinate point with a latitude, longitude, and altitude
    HashInfo
    Contains the generated information for a given hash
    Player
    Represents a user with an id, username, contact info, preferences, and scannable codes
    PlayerList
    Represents a container for all the players in game right now
    PlayerPreferences
    Contains a player's current preferences
    PlayerWallet
    Represents a list of the player's current scanned codes
    ScannableCode
    Represents a scannable code that can be scanned and contains information about the code and comments by users.
